              <text x="447" y="222" fill="#7c3aed" font-size="11.5" font-style="italic" text-anchor="middle">se enseña en contexto natural;</text>
              <text x="447" y="240" fill="#7c3aed" font-size="11.5" font-style="italic" text-anchor="middle">se generaliza al hogar</text>
